{"title":"大庆红旗飘炉前","authors":["王德祥"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":3,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆红旗飘炉前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首都钢铁公司工人  王德祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里，没有井架的森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里，没有炼塔的群山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里，只有转炉的长岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里，只有高炉的峰巅……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却为啥呵却为啥——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处唱大庆的号子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处敲大庆的鼓点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处都展现大庆的场面？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却为啥呵却为啥——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处迈铁人的步子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处有铁人的容颜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处回荡铁人的呐喊？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因为，党中央发出动员令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里钢城掀烈焰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因为，钢铁工人学大庆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆红旗飘炉前！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}